        * platform/graphics/FontPlatformData.h:
        * platform/graphics/cocoa/FontPlatformDataCocoa.mm:
        * platform/graphics/freetype/FontPlatformDataFreeType.cpp:
        * platform/graphics/win/FontPlatformDataWin.cpp:

