            (WebCore::DocumentLoader::cancelPolicyCheckIfNeeded): Cancel the policy check if there is one.
            (WebCore::DocumentLoader::cancelMainResourceLoad): Use cancelPolicyCheckIfNeeded().
            * loader/DocumentLoader.h:

